<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>日本酒造資料庫｜Sakego</title>
<meta name="description" content="探索 {{ total_breweries }} 家日本酒造、{{ total_products }} 款銘柄,按地區瀏覽。">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ page_path }}styles.css">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="site-title"><a href="{{ page_path }}index.html">日本酒造資料庫</a></h1>
    <p class="site-tagline">Sakego ｜ 探索 {{ total_breweries }} 家酒造、{{ total_products }} 款日本酒</p>
  </div>
</header>

{# ===== 滿版奢華 Hero - 完全照 Claude Design ===== #}
<section class="home-hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1597290282695-edc43d0e7129?w=1600&q=85');"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-texture"></div>
  <div class="hero-vignette"></div>
  <div class="hero-deco-kanji">酒</div>

  {# 垂直裝飾文字 - 照 Claude Design 文案 #}
  <div class="hero-vert-text">清酒 · 純米 · 吟釀 · 大吟釀 · 本醸造 · 風土</div>

  {# 12 顆金色光點粒子 - 精準位置 #}
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 12%; bottom: 18%; width: 8px; height: 8px; --dur: 4.2s; --delay: 0s; --dx: 18px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 22%; bottom: 8%; width: 5px; height: 5px; --dur: 5.1s; --delay: 1.2s; --dx: -14px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 35%; bottom: 25%; width: 10px; height: 10px; --dur: 3.8s; --delay: 2.4s; --dx: 24px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 48%; bottom: 12%; width: 6px; height: 6px; --dur: 4.8s; --delay: 0.6s; --dx: -20px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 58%; bottom: 30%; width: 4px; height: 4px; --dur: 6.0s; --delay: 1.8s; --dx: 12px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 70%; bottom: 10%; width: 9px; height: 9px; --dur: 4.4s; --delay: 3.0s; --dx: -16px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 80%; bottom: 22%; width: 5px; height: 5px; --dur: 5.5s; --delay: 0.3s; --dx: 22px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 18%; bottom: 40%; width: 4px; height: 4px; --dur: 3.6s; --delay: 2.1s; --dx: -10px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 42%; bottom: 45%; width: 7px; height: 7px; --dur: 5.2s; --delay: 1.5s; --dx: 18px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 65%; bottom: 38%; width: 5px; height: 5px; --dur: 4.0s; --delay: 3.6s; --dx: -22px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 88%; bottom: 15%; width: 6px; height: 6px; --dur: 4.9s; --delay: 0.9s; --dx: 14px;"></div>
  <div class="hero-bokeh" style="left: 28%; bottom: 55%; width: 3px; height: 3px; --dur: 6.2s; --delay: 4.2s; --dx: -8px;"></div>

  {# 漂浮的酒瓶卡 - 桌機右側 #}
  <div class="hero-float-card">
    <div class="float-card-inner">
      <div class="float-card-label">JUNMAI</div>
      <div class="float-card-name">磯自慢</div>
      <div class="float-card-jp">いそじまん</div>
      <div class="float-card-divider"></div>
      <div class="float-card-brewery">磯自慢酒造</div>
      <div class="float-card-area">SHIZUOKA</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {# 主要內容 - 對齊 Claude Design,右側留漂浮卡空間 #}
  <div class="container hero-content hero-content-with-card">
    <span class="hero-eyebrow hero-anim-1">Sakego ｜ 日本酒造資料庫</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title hero-anim-2">
      探索<span class="hero-shimmer">日本酒</span><br>的世界
    </h1>
    <div class="hero-ornament hero-anim-3">
      <span class="hero-orn-dot"></span>
      <span class="hero-orn-line"></span>
      <span class="hero-orn-dia"></span>
      <span class="hero-orn-dot"></span>
      <span class="hero-orn-dia"></span>
      <span class="hero-orn-line r"></span>
      <span class="hero-orn-dot"></span>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-sub hero-anim-3">從北海道到九州,{{ total_breweries }} 家酒造、{{ total_products }} 款銘柄,一次掌握</p>
    <div class="hero-search hero-anim-4">
      <input type="search" id="search-input" placeholder="搜尋酒造、銘柄或地區⋯" autocomplete="off">
      <div id="search-results" class="search-results" hidden></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {# 玻璃霧化統計條 (置底) - 數字加 + 號 #}
  <div class="hero-stats-strip hero-anim-4">
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <span class="hero-stat-num">{{ total_breweries }}+</span>
      <span class="hero-stat-label">酒造</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <span class="hero-stat-num">{{ total_products }}+</span>
      <span class="hero-stat-label">銘柄</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <span class="hero-stat-num">{{ regions|length }}</span>
      <span class="hero-stat-label">地區</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== 品牌宣言 - 完整版含背景巨字 + 主標 + 副標 ===== #}
<section class="manifesto-strip">
  <div class="manifesto-deco">酒造</div>
  <div class="container">
    <span class="manifesto-eyebrow">我們的信念</span>
    <p class="manifesto-text">
      「&ensp;從產地到杯中,每一滴都有故事。&ensp;」
      <span class="manifesto-sub">
        土壤、水、米、酵母——四者共同書寫一款清酒的風土個性。Sakego 讓你讀懂每一瓶的語言。
      </span>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<main>
  {# ===== 地區英雄榜 - 對齊 Claude Design 文案 ===== #}
  <div class="container">
    <section class="rankings-section">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">地區英雄榜</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">各地風土,按酒造數排行</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">點擊任一地區,深入探索當地酒造與銘柄</p>
      <div class="rank-grid">
        {% set max_count = regions | map(attribute='brewery_count') | max %}
        {% for region in regions %}
        <a href="{{ page_path }}regions/{{ region.name | safe_id }}/" class="rank-card">
          <span class="rank-card-accent"></span>
          <span class="rank-num-bg">{{ "%02d"|format(loop.index) }}</span>
          <span class="rank-ordinal">No. {{ "%02d"|format(loop.index) }}</span>
          <h3 class="rank-name">{{ region.name }}</h3>
          <p class="rank-prefectures">
            {% set areas_list = region.areas.keys() | list %}
            {{ areas_list[:5] | join(' · ') }}{% if areas_list|length > 5 %} · ⋯{% endif %}
          </p>
          <div class="rank-bar-track">
            <div class="rank-bar-fill" style="width: {{ (region.brewery_count / max_count * 100) | int }}%;"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="rank-count"><strong>{{ region.brewery_count }}</strong> 家酒造</p>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  {# ===== 銘柄英雄榜 - 黑底得獎排行 ===== #}
  {% if featured_products %}
  <div style="background: var(--secondary); padding: 72px 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow" style="color: var(--accent);">銘柄英雄榜</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="color: #fff; margin-bottom: 8px;">精選推薦銘柄</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin: 0 0 40px; letter-spacing: 0.04em;">
        依星級推薦與國際競賽得獎數綜合排名
      </p>
      <div class="brand-rank-grid">
        {% for product in featured_products[:10] %}
        <a href="{{ page_path }}products/{{ product.product_id | safe_id }}.html" class="brand-rank-row">
          <div class="brand-rank-num">{{ "%02d"|format(loop.index) }}</div>
          <div>
            <p class="brand-rank-name">{{ product.name_zhtw or product.name_jp }}</p>
            <p class="brand-rank-meta">
              {{ product.brewery_name_jp }} ·
              {{ product.area_zhtw or product.area_jp }}{% if product.sake_type %} ·
              {{ product.sake_type }}{% endif %}
            </p>
            {% if product._awards %}
            <p class="brand-rank-meta" style="margin-top: 4px; color: var(--accent);">
              🏆 {{ product._awards[:2] | join(' · ') }}{% if product._awards|length > 2 %} +{{ product._awards|length - 2 }}{% endif %}
            </p>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="brand-rank-stars">
            {% for i in range(5) %}
              <span class="star {% if i < product._stars %}full{% else %}empty{% endif %}">★</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {# ===== 精選酒造 Spotlight ===== #}
  {% if spotlight_breweries %}
  <div class="container">
    <section class="spotlight-section">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">精選酒造</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 36px;">值得深探的名門</h2>
      {% for brewery in spotlight_breweries %}
      <a href="{{ page_path }}breweries/{{ brewery.brewery_id | safe_id }}.html"
         class="spotlight-panel{% if loop.index % 2 == 0 %} flipped{% endif %}">
        <div class="spotlight-img">
          <img src="{{ brewery._hero_image }}" alt="{{ brewery.name_jp }}" loading="lazy">
          <div class="spotlight-img-overlay"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="spotlight-body">
          <span class="spotlight-eyebrow">精選酒造</span>
          <h3 class="spotlight-title">{{ brewery.name_zhtw or brewery.name_jp }}</h3>
          {% if brewery.name_zhtw and brewery.name_zhtw != brewery.name_jp %}
          <p class="spotlight-jp">{{ brewery.name_jp }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="spotlight-meta">
            <span>📍 {{ brewery.area_zhtw or brewery.area_jp }}</span>
            {% if brewery.founded_year %}<span>🏯 創業 {{ brewery.founded_year }}</span>{% endif %}
            <span>🍶 {{ brewery._products | length }} 款銘柄</span>
          </div>
          <span class="spotlight-cta">探索銘柄 &nbsp;›</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </section>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {# ===== 各地區酒造 - 統一網格 (照 Claude Design 不分 area 子組) ===== #}
  <div class="container">
    {% for region in regions %}
    <section class="region-block" id="region-{{ region.name | safe_id }}">
      <header class="region-header">
        <h2><a href="{{ page_path }}regions/{{ region.name | safe_id }}/">{{ region.name }}</a></h2>
        <span class="region-count">{{ region.brewery_count }} 家酒造</span>
      </header>

      {# 全部酒造放在一個統一網格,不再用 area 細分 #}
      {# 大地區(>30家)只顯示前 30 家避免畫面太長,連結到地區頁看完整 #}
      <div class="brewery-entries">
        {% set all_breweries = [] %}
        {% for area, breweries in region.areas.items() %}
          {% for brewery in breweries %}
            {% set display_name = (brewery.name_zhtw or brewery.name_jp or '') | trim %}
            {% if display_name %}
              {% set _ = all_breweries.append({'brewery': brewery, 'area': area, 'name': display_name}) %}
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        {% endfor %}

        {% for item in all_breweries[:30] %}
        <a href="{{ page_path }}breweries/{{ item.brewery.brewery_id | safe_id }}.html" class="brewery-entry">
          <div class="brewery-entry-body">
            <span class="brewery-entry-name">{{ item.name }}</span>
            {% if item.brewery.name_zhtw and item.brewery.name_zhtw != item.brewery.name_jp %}
            <span class="brewery-entry-jp">{{ item.brewery.name_jp }}</span>
            {% endif %}
            <span class="brewery-entry-count">{{ item.brewery.area_zhtw or item.area }}</span>
          </div>
          <span class="brewery-entry-arrow">›</span>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      {% if all_breweries|length > 30 %}
      <p style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{ page_path }}regions/{{ region.name | safe_id }}/" style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 500;">
          查看 {{ region.name }} 全部 {{ all_breweries|length }} 家酒造 →
        </a>
      </p>
      {% endif %}
    </section>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container">
    <p>資料來源:<a href="https://sakenowa.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Sakenowa Data Project</a>｜事實規格欄位來自各酒造官網</p>
    <p class="footer-meta">情境圖片來自 <a href="https://unsplash.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Unsplash</a>(CC0/Unsplash License)</p>
    <p class="footer-meta">最後更新:{{ generated_at }}</p>
  </div>
</footer>

{% include '_warning_bar.html.j2' %}

<script src="{{ page_path }}search.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
